# IOT_Team Name

## Overview

Accessible E-Rickshaw Automation System â€” enables elderly and special needs users to request rickshaws with smart block units and web dashboards.

## 1. Hardware Setup
- Wire up sensors: ultrasound, LDR, button, LEDs to ESP32.
- Upload firmware (`user_code.ino`).
- Connect to WiFi (edit credentials in code).

## 2. Backend Setup
- Install Node.js 18+.
- `npm install`
- `node server.js`

## 3. Rickshaw Web-app
- `cd rickshaw-app`
- `npm install`
- `npm start`

## 4. Admin Dashboard
- `cd admin-dashboard`
- `npm install`
- `npm start`

## 5. Usage
- Stand on block, press button.
- Rickshaw puller sees new request in web-app and can accept.
- Admin monitors rides in dashboard.

## 6. Configuration
- Edit `.env` for API keys, ports etc as needed.

## 7. Support
- Include screenshots, troubleshooting, contact email.
